1
00:01:00,439 --> 00:01:01,560
Six sixes, eight horses!

2
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:02,600
Seven champions!

3
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:03,640
Come on!

4
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:04,280
Drink!

5
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:06,280
Drink!

6
00:01:07,239 --> 00:01:08,040
Fill it up!

7
00:01:08,159 --> 00:01:09,959
Fill it up, fill it up!

8
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:18,200
Come on!

9
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:20,680
Like I'm scared of you!

10
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:21,480
Come on!

11
00:01:24,239 --> 00:01:25,280
Drink up!

12
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:26,480
Hey, you lot!

13
00:01:26,799 --> 00:01:28,159
Is Number Seven here?

14
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:31,040
No, no.

15
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:32,799
Oh, come on.

16
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:38,239
No Number Seven, huh?

17
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:40,359
Let's all go at him!

18
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:41,400
Brothers!

19
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:42,840
Let's take him together!

20
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:43,640
Come on!

21
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:44,400
We outnumber him, no need to fear!

22
00:01:45,439 --> 00:01:46,000
Come on!

23
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:46,599
Come on!

24
00:01:46,599 --> 00:01:47,400
Bottoms up!

25
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,680
Drunk already?

26
00:01:56,879 --> 00:01:57,680
Keep drinking!

27
00:02:11,639 --> 00:02:12,439
Heh.

28
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,400
None of them can hold their liquor.

29
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:16,639
Number Seven.

30
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:19,280
I'm going to find you, no matter what.

31
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:26,199
These guys aren't dead, are they?

32
00:02:26,199 --> 00:02:27,280
Zhenzhen, don't be afraid.

33
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,240
I'll protect you.

34
00:02:36,599 --> 00:02:37,479
They're not dead.

35
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:39,879
Probably just had too much to drink.

36
00:02:40,879 --> 00:02:42,039
Too much to drink?

37
00:02:42,039 --> 00:02:44,039
Drinking heavily while on duty?

38
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:45,560
That's so irresponsible!

39
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,560
Speaking of irresponsible,

40
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:47,759
who could ever top you?

41
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,039
Wow.

42
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:53,560
It really is the City of Wine.

43
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:56,280
Even the guards drink ten-year Peach Blossom Wine.

44
00:02:59,479 --> 00:03:00,879
But I've quit drinking.

45
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:02,879
Ugh.

46
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:04,639
That smells awful!

47
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,280
Nuerhong!

48
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,000
But I've quit drinking.

49
00:03:12,199 --> 00:03:12,800
Hey, Qi Zhi.

50
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:14,439
Didn't know you were such a wine connoisseur.

51
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,759
I know a thing or two.

52
00:03:17,039 --> 00:03:18,080
But I've quit drinking.

53
00:03:18,479 --> 00:03:19,360
Since you're not drinking,

54
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,680
let's hurry inside and find him.

55
00:03:21,159 --> 00:03:22,159
Let's go in first.

56
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:26,840
Stop staring.

57
00:03:29,199 --> 00:03:32,560
One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

58
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:35,639
Two, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

59
00:03:35,759 --> 00:03:38,560
Three, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

60
00:03:38,599 --> 00:03:39,840
Doctor, Doctor, Doctor!

61
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:40,360
Hold on a moment.

62
00:03:40,599 --> 00:03:41,479
Stop pressing!

63
00:03:41,479 --> 00:03:42,439
I'm awake.

64
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:45,400
That's just the alcohol talking.

65
00:03:45,599 --> 00:03:47,759
You must continue your treatment!

66
00:03:48,159 --> 00:03:48,919
No, wait...

67
00:03:48,919 --> 00:03:49,800
Doctor.

68
00:03:50,439 --> 00:03:51,479
Doctor!

69
00:03:51,479 --> 00:03:51,680
If you keep pressing,

70
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:53,840
you're going to press me to death!

71
00:03:54,199 --> 00:03:55,560
Are you sure you can still drink?

72
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:56,639
I...

73
00:03:57,639 --> 00:03:58,439
No problem.

74
00:03:58,439 --> 00:03:59,639
I can still drink.

75
00:04:00,439 --> 00:04:01,240
Eight hundred jars!

76
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,759
He's beyond saving!

77
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:04,840
Quick!

78
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,240
Begin electric shock treatment immediately!

79
00:04:06,639 --> 00:04:07,039
Right!

80
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,840
What are you doing?

81
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:09,960
Doctor!

82
00:04:10,159 --> 00:04:10,479
Take this!

83
00:04:10,639 --> 00:04:11,639
What are you doing?

84
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,639
Doctor! Doctor! Doctor!

85
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:14,879
Don't do anything reckless!

86
00:04:14,879 --> 00:04:15,680
What are you doing?

87
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:17,360
Doctor!

88
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:17,879
Aaah!

89
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,279
Another life saved!

90
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,199
Doctor...

91
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,839
He's still conscious.

92
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,439
Begin Emetic Therapy immediately.

93
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,399
Make him vomit a few more times.

94
00:04:47,399 --> 00:04:48,639
And he should be fine.

95
00:04:48,759 --> 00:04:49,560
Mm.

96
00:04:52,639 --> 00:04:53,480
Hey.

97
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:55,000
It's all right.

98
00:04:55,139 --> 00:04:55,839
It's red wine.

99
00:04:56,539 --> 00:04:56,980
Doctor.

100
00:04:57,180 --> 00:04:57,939
What's going on

101
00:04:57,939 --> 00:04:58,880
here in Duzun City?

102
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:05,160
You must be outsiders.

103
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,480
Then there's a lot you don't know.

104
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:11,480
The Lord of Duzun passed away a few days ago.

105
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:14,160
Now the Sole Goblet Tournament is being held.

106
00:05:14,959 --> 00:05:16,040
Whoever wins

107
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,680
becomes the next City Lord.

108
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,040
Liu Lie is dead?

109
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:21,839
Who's Liu Lie?

110
00:05:22,439 --> 00:05:24,160
Liu Lie is your City Lord, King Lie.

111
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:25,480
Huh?

112
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:27,240
Our City Lord's surname isn't Liu.

113
00:05:27,839 --> 00:05:29,079
Here in Duzun City,

114
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,600
whoever drinks the most

115
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:33,240
becomes the City Lord.

116
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:35,560
Right now,

117
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,839
gods of wine from all around

118
00:05:36,839 --> 00:05:38,240
have gathered here.

119
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:40,839
It's truly a clash of champions,

120
00:05:41,439 --> 00:05:42,839
and the battles are brutal.

121
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:46,480
Men who drink are so unreliable.

122
00:05:48,839 --> 00:05:51,079
I really don't want to marry someone like that.

123
00:05:51,839 --> 00:05:53,240
You shouldn't say that.

124
00:05:53,399 --> 00:05:54,680
As the saying goes,

125
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,480
a little drink is a pleasure,

126
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,839
it's heavy drinking that's harmful.

127
00:05:56,839 --> 00:05:58,399
Well said.

128
00:05:58,839 --> 00:05:59,839
If nothing else,

129
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:02,079
just the wine used for this contest

130
00:06:02,839 --> 00:06:06,480
is Huadiao Vintage aged at least 15 years.

131
00:06:07,839 --> 00:06:09,079
Then let's go find him quickly.

132
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,480
Even though I've quit drinking,

133
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:11,959
Qi Zhi, if you like wine...

134
00:06:11,959 --> 00:06:12,279
Zhenzhen,

135
00:06:12,279 --> 00:06:13,800
let's talk business first.

136
00:06:14,279 --> 00:06:14,920
Doctor,

137
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,839
do you know where Liu Lie is?

138
00:06:21,439 --> 00:06:23,160
Such a juicy prize

139
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:26,160
just delivered itself to our door.

140
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,360
You want it?

141
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,680
Ten days ago,

142
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,639
I heard a Prince entered the Wine Duel Arena.

143
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:43,480
But there's been no word since.

144
00:06:44,079 --> 00:06:45,079
No word?

145
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:47,360
So that means

146
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,680
his life may very well be in danger.

147
00:06:51,079 --> 00:06:52,560
At this Sole Goblet Tournament,

148
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:54,240
a Masked Master has shown up.

149
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,519
These people,

150
00:06:56,519 --> 00:06:59,480
eighty percent of them were drunk under the table by him.

151
00:07:01,439 --> 00:07:02,240
What?

152
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:04,879
Drinking could cost you your life?

153
00:07:05,079 --> 00:07:06,439
Then we'd better leave, fast.

154
00:07:06,639 --> 00:07:07,199
Since we're already here,

155
00:07:07,199 --> 00:07:08,279
let's go in and look for him.

156
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,240
Hey, Doctor.

157
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:10,480
Uh...

158
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,680
Would you mind coming along with us?

159
00:07:13,959 --> 00:07:14,759
Oh.

160
00:07:20,639 --> 00:07:23,199
I've practiced medicine half my life,

161
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,800
To heal and save lives,

162
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:26,439
rescuing the dying and healing the wounded.

163
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,560
I've never set foot in a drinking arena.

164
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,639
I'm afraid I must decline.

165
00:07:32,199 --> 00:07:32,879
Doctor.

166
00:07:32,879 --> 00:07:33,879
A hundred thousand taels.

167
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:37,480
Sigh.

168
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:44,800
Very well.

169
00:07:45,399 --> 00:07:47,639
I'll take you in for a bit of fun.

170
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:49,600
However,

171
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:52,160
the arena only admits newcomers at night.

172
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:55,480
So wait with me until nightfall.

173
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:56,839
Why's that?

174
00:07:57,199 --> 00:07:58,399
Hahaha!

175
00:07:59,439 --> 00:08:04,000
Because nighttime is the prime hour for drinking.

176
00:08:13,279 --> 00:08:14,800
The rules are simple.

177
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:16,480
Uh...

178
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,680
As long as you drink him under the table,

179
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,759
you can claim his token.

180
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:23,800
In the end,

181
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:26,040
whoever has the most tokens

182
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,959
becomes the new City Lord.

183
00:08:31,079 --> 00:08:31,879
Ah.

184
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:34,639
Going by Liu Lie's tolerance as a child,

185
00:08:34,759 --> 00:08:36,200
among the top two,

186
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:36,879
one of them has to be him.

187
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:39,480
The smell of liquor's so strong,

188
00:08:39,759 --> 00:08:41,200
it's making me dizzy just smelling it.

189
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,480
How are we supposed to find anyone here?

190
00:08:45,279 --> 00:08:46,159
Hey, Qi Zhi.

191
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:48,159
Look, isn't that Liu Lie?

192
00:08:48,279 --> 00:08:49,080
Hey!

193
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,240
The two of you,

194
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,200
clinging onto each other,

195
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,240
how unseemly!

196
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,200
Exactly.

197
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:53,559
Forget it.

198
00:08:53,559 --> 00:08:54,840
Let's just

199
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:55,799
split up and search separately.

200
00:08:55,799 --> 00:08:56,600
Sounds good.

201
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:57,759
It's settled then.

202
00:08:58,799 --> 00:08:59,600
Doctor.

203
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:00,679
Hey!

204
00:09:13,679 --> 00:09:14,960
What's going on?

205
00:09:15,559 --> 00:09:17,000
Sorry about that.

206
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,080
How lucky.

207
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:28,159
Just woke up and already found new prey.

208
00:09:28,639 --> 00:09:29,440
Come on.

209
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:30,840
Have a drink.

210
00:09:34,039 --> 00:09:34,840
Drink up.

211
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:35,759
I don't drink.

212
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,399
You two, stand back.

213
00:09:40,159 --> 00:09:41,759
Leave her to me.

214
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,240
Bring it on!

215
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:58,240
How vulgar.

216
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:01,080
That's not how wine drinkers do it.

217
00:10:02,399 --> 00:10:03,399
Watch me.

218
00:10:05,639 --> 00:10:06,440
Here.

219
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,240
Fine wine!

220
00:10:21,679 --> 00:10:22,480
Ah!

221
00:10:22,799 --> 00:10:23,600
Hey!

222
00:10:25,559 --> 00:10:28,559
What an unreliable teammate!

223
00:10:28,759 --> 00:10:30,799
Well, you're the one who recruited him.

224
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:34,440
It's your turn now, right?

225
00:10:34,759 --> 00:10:35,679
What do we do?

226
00:10:35,679 --> 00:10:37,679
I really can't drink.

227
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:39,759
Honestly, I can't hold my liquor either.

228
00:10:40,279 --> 00:10:41,240
Cut the nonsense.

229
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:43,399
If you can't drink, hand over your token.

230
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:46,000
We really don't drink.

231
00:10:46,039 --> 00:10:46,639
Hmm.

232
00:10:46,639 --> 00:10:47,440
Oh.

233
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:50,480
In the Wine Duel Arena, only wine settles disputes.

234
00:10:50,879 --> 00:10:52,080
Force is strictly forbidden.

235
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,600
Anyone who breaks the rules

236
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:55,200
will be expelled from the arena.

237
00:10:56,039 --> 00:10:57,679
Which of your eyes

238
00:10:57,679 --> 00:10:58,879
saw me using force?

239
00:10:58,879 --> 00:10:59,679
Exactly!

240
00:11:00,759 --> 00:11:02,000
I was just peeling an apple.

241
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:05,200
Drink this.

242
00:11:06,039 --> 00:11:06,840
What is it?

243
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,320
Skill-Nullifying Wine.

244
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,559
Once you drink it,

245
00:11:09,559 --> 00:11:11,440
you'll temporarily lose all your martial arts.

246
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:13,799
Sir,

247
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:15,799
she really can't drink.

248
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:17,200
You see,

249
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:17,799
how about...

250
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:22,960
I think you're just too scared to drink it.

251
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:24,879
Hahaha!

252
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:28,480
Hey!

253
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,360
It's just a sip of wine.

254
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:35,000
You think I'm scared of you?

255
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:41,940
Hey, hey, hey!

256
00:11:43,540 --> 00:11:44,380
What's going on here?

257
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:45,600
Couldn't you see it was reverse psychology?

258
00:11:47,199 --> 00:11:49,000
Drink this jar of mine first!

259
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:53,399
I can still drink.

260
00:11:55,679 --> 00:11:57,559
I've endured bitter struggle for over a decade.

261
00:11:58,000 --> 00:12:00,039
Not just to lose to the likes of you.

262
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:22,180
Careful!

263
00:12:22,280 --> 00:12:22,640
Are you okay?

264
00:12:22,640 --> 00:12:23,200
Come on, come on.

265
00:12:23,240 --> 00:12:24,120
Hey, girl!

266
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:25,879
Stop right there, don't run!

267
00:12:28,879 --> 00:12:31,399
Have one more jar with Jiu Niang!

268
00:12:34,279 --> 00:12:35,639
I'll drink in her place.

269
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:38,240
You came here and you don't drink?

270
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,200
What are you doing?

271
00:12:39,759 --> 00:12:40,399
Qi Zhi!

272
00:12:40,399 --> 00:12:41,200
Wait a minute.

273
00:12:42,559 --> 00:12:43,679
Come drink!

274
00:12:47,159 --> 00:12:48,279
I'll be your opponent.

275
00:12:48,960 --> 00:12:50,440
Meat at my lips,

276
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:52,240
there's no reason not to eat it.

277
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:53,240
Hmph.

278
00:13:01,039 --> 00:13:01,960
What is she doing?

279
00:13:03,679 --> 00:13:04,799
Silver Needle Detox.

280
00:13:05,039 --> 00:13:06,279
Just a petty trick.

281
00:13:09,799 --> 00:13:10,879
This isn't drinking,

282
00:13:10,879 --> 00:13:12,240
this is risking your life!

283
00:13:17,039 --> 00:13:17,840
Hmph!

284
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:19,240
Here!

285
00:13:20,039 --> 00:13:20,840
Come on!

286
00:13:21,279 --> 00:13:22,600
Is that Liu Lie?

287
00:13:22,679 --> 00:13:23,559
No.

288
00:13:29,879 --> 00:13:30,559
Zhenzhen.

289
00:13:30,559 --> 00:13:31,159
Yes?

290
00:13:31,159 --> 00:13:33,360
The comic I recently updated,

291
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:33,879
have you read it?

292
00:13:33,879 --> 00:13:34,679
I have.

293
00:13:35,399 --> 00:13:36,360
Did you like it?

294
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:37,360
I loved it.

295
00:13:38,360 --> 00:13:39,159
Really?

296
00:13:39,639 --> 00:13:41,279
I knew you'd love it.

297
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:43,279
Hey, Zhenzhen,

298
00:13:43,399 --> 00:13:44,360
what else do you want to read?

299
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:45,480
I'll keep drawing for you.

300
00:13:45,639 --> 00:13:47,399
Hey, look, isn't that Liu Lie?

301
00:13:47,799 --> 00:13:48,759
No, no, it's not.

302
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:50,399
Zhenzhen.

303
00:13:50,679 --> 00:13:51,840
Hmm?

304
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:53,039
What were you saying about a comic?

305
00:13:55,879 --> 00:13:57,519
Nothing.

306
00:13:57,519 --> 00:13:58,080
Let's keep looking.

307
00:14:08,759 --> 00:14:09,159
Drink!

308
00:14:09,159 --> 00:14:09,960
Come on!

309
00:14:19,879 --> 00:14:20,519
How's that?

310
00:14:20,519 --> 00:14:21,159
Doing okay?

311
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:23,240
Keep it coming.

312
00:14:31,279 --> 00:14:32,200
All gone.

313
00:14:58,679 --> 00:14:59,480
Drink!

314
00:15:13,399 --> 00:15:15,219
Many thanks, hero,

315
00:15:15,219 --> 00:15:15,799
for your righteous help.

316
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:17,039
You two take me on together.

317
00:15:17,039 --> 00:15:17,639
I'm in a hurry.

318
00:15:17,639 --> 00:15:18,639
You drink first.

319
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:20,200
We don't drink.

320
00:15:20,759 --> 00:15:21,279
I quit.

321
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:25,799
Number Seven.

322
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:27,720
Wait a moment.

323
00:15:27,720 --> 00:15:28,799
Are you Liu Lie?

324
00:15:31,159 --> 00:15:32,000
You know me?

325
00:15:32,559 --> 00:15:33,399
Mm.

326
00:15:33,679 --> 00:15:34,679
Yes, yes, I know you.

327
00:15:35,159 --> 00:15:36,039
Even so, you still have to drink.

328
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:43,480
Are you alright?

329
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:47,960
This Liu Lie is so unreliable.

330
00:15:50,799 --> 00:15:53,240
The Crown Prince once told me

331
00:15:54,679 --> 00:15:56,279
he's loved drinking since childhood.

332
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:58,840
The Late Emperor really disliked him.

333
00:15:59,639 --> 00:16:02,000
He never accepted any fief either,

334
00:16:02,039 --> 00:16:05,559
and came alone to Duzun City.

335
00:16:05,879 --> 00:16:09,440
Just to win the City Lord's seat by drinking.

336
00:16:10,120 --> 00:16:10,960
Burp.

337
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:12,679
Quite a backbone, huh.

338
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:15,480
But after hearing the Crown Prince say that,

339
00:16:16,039 --> 00:16:18,480
I worry he won't want to return to the palace

340
00:16:21,120 --> 00:16:23,799
to inherit the throne.

341
00:16:24,480 --> 00:16:25,480
Well then,

342
00:16:25,679 --> 00:16:27,639
let's wait until he gets drunk

343
00:16:28,240 --> 00:16:29,679
and have him sign the document.

344
00:16:30,080 --> 00:16:31,600
Then he can't go back on it.

345
00:16:33,159 --> 00:16:35,039
You even prepared a document?

346
00:16:35,679 --> 00:16:37,240
After failing so many times,

347
00:16:37,240 --> 00:16:38,600
shouldn't I have learned a lesson?

348
00:16:38,799 --> 00:16:38,960
Wow.

349
00:16:38,960 --> 00:16:41,279
This woman's even more cunning than me.

350
00:16:42,039 --> 00:16:42,720
No way.

351
00:16:42,720 --> 00:16:43,879
I have to do something.

352
00:16:47,039 --> 00:16:47,279
Uh.

353
00:16:47,279 --> 00:16:49,200
Prince Liu Lie,

354
00:16:49,679 --> 00:16:51,240
actually, the two of us...

355
00:16:51,240 --> 00:16:52,039
No need to say more.

356
00:16:52,279 --> 00:16:54,480
You were so loud, I heard everything.

357
00:16:55,879 --> 00:16:56,679
So that means

358
00:16:56,679 --> 00:16:57,960
you agree?

359
00:16:58,360 --> 00:16:59,159
I don't agree.

360
00:16:59,639 --> 00:17:00,440
Why not?

361
00:17:02,360 --> 00:17:03,360
Once you become Emperor,

362
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:05,680
forget Duzun City,

363
00:17:06,079 --> 00:17:07,680
all the wine in the realm is yours.

364
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:10,799
Even if I become Emperor,

365
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:13,599
I must first win the City Lord's seat.

366
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:18,240
Oh-ho.

367
00:17:19,279 --> 00:17:20,960
So you're Number Seven.

368
00:17:21,200 --> 00:17:21,839
Hahaha.

369
00:17:21,839 --> 00:17:22,680
Today,

370
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:25,200
we, The Ten, want to challenge you.

371
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:26,759
Of all the times to show up,

372
00:17:26,759 --> 00:17:28,160
they had to come right now.

373
00:17:31,200 --> 00:17:32,000
Hey.

374
00:17:40,160 --> 00:17:42,240
You're ganging up on one man.

375
00:17:43,039 --> 00:17:44,279
Even if you win,

376
00:17:44,279 --> 00:17:45,480
it'd be a dishonorable victory.

377
00:17:45,680 --> 00:17:46,599
Hahahaha.

378
00:17:47,079 --> 00:17:48,640
Just a bunch of rabble.

379
00:17:49,880 --> 00:17:51,039
Why be afraid of them?

380
00:18:01,799 --> 00:18:02,599
Wow.

381
00:18:05,680 --> 00:18:07,480
I think we can win this.

382
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:10,279
I'm not so sure.

383
00:18:13,880 --> 00:18:14,680
Hey, hey, hey!

384
00:18:18,119 --> 00:18:18,559
Run!

385
00:18:18,559 --> 00:18:19,000
Go!

386
00:18:21,039 --> 00:18:21,599
Hurry, hurry!

387
00:18:21,839 --> 00:18:23,200
What are you standing there for?

388
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:24,160
After him!

389
00:18:29,839 --> 00:18:32,359
Since he's now unconscious,

390
00:18:33,400 --> 00:18:34,279
why don't we...

391
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:43,000
Hey!

392
00:18:44,599 --> 00:18:46,559
You're taking advantage of the situation!

393
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:56,480
Stop right there!

394
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:01,559
As a court official,

395
00:19:01,640 --> 00:19:03,640
how dare you commit such a vile act!

396
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:06,680
If I, the herald of justice, hadn't arrived in time,

397
00:19:07,279 --> 00:19:09,720
your scheme would've already succeeded.

398
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:10,960
Hmph.

399
00:19:11,839 --> 00:19:13,039
Mind your own business.

400
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:15,039
Your powers are completely gone now.

401
00:19:15,200 --> 00:19:16,279
I'm not afraid of you.

402
00:19:19,279 --> 00:19:19,920
Brothers!

403
00:19:19,920 --> 00:19:21,880
Come lend me a helping hand!

404
00:19:31,240 --> 00:19:32,039
Hmm.

405
00:19:41,799 --> 00:19:42,599
Hmph.

406
00:19:43,640 --> 00:19:45,160
Hand over Liu Lie to me!

407
00:19:45,400 --> 00:19:46,200
Who?

408
00:19:46,559 --> 00:19:47,759
Huh?

409
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:51,799
Why am I here?

410
00:19:51,880 --> 00:19:52,640
Uh, he...

411
00:19:53,480 --> 00:19:54,480
He provoked you.

412
00:19:54,680 --> 00:19:55,279
Hey!

413
00:19:55,279 --> 00:19:55,680
You!

414
00:19:55,880 --> 00:19:56,480
Oh dear.

415
00:19:56,480 --> 00:19:58,640
You can't out-drink me.

416
00:19:58,839 --> 00:20:00,279
Don't waste your effort.

417
00:20:00,559 --> 00:20:01,400
The position of City Lord

418
00:20:01,400 --> 00:20:02,599
will surely be mine.

419
00:20:06,279 --> 00:20:07,680
So it's you, kid.

420
00:20:08,640 --> 00:20:09,480
Oh, Imperial Brother.

421
00:20:09,559 --> 00:20:10,799
Please don't misunderstand.

422
00:20:10,880 --> 00:20:12,039
My coming here today

423
00:20:12,039 --> 00:20:13,160
has no other meaning.

424
00:20:13,200 --> 00:20:14,839
I simply wanted to

425
00:20:14,839 --> 00:20:16,039
catch up with you.

426
00:20:16,079 --> 00:20:16,880
Haha.

427
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:17,480
Catch up, eh?

428
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:21,759
Come on!

429
00:20:22,279 --> 00:20:23,039
Come on!

430
00:20:38,480 --> 00:20:39,680
One more!

431
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:40,440
Come on!

432
00:20:44,640 --> 00:20:45,480
You okay?

433
00:20:49,680 --> 00:20:50,480
Come on!

434
00:20:50,839 --> 00:20:51,640
Come on!

435
00:20:58,039 --> 00:20:58,880
Drink!

436
00:20:59,680 --> 00:21:00,480
Drink it!

437
00:21:06,279 --> 00:21:07,039
Keep going!

438
00:21:07,079 --> 00:21:07,559
Come on!

439
00:21:07,559 --> 00:21:08,000
Come on!

440
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:09,480
Bottoms up!

441
00:21:09,480 --> 00:21:10,279
Cheers!

442
00:21:29,759 --> 00:21:30,559
Cheers!

443
00:21:34,039 --> 00:21:34,359
Hey, Imperial Brother.

444
00:21:34,839 --> 00:21:35,119
You see,

445
00:21:35,279 --> 00:21:36,200
it's getting pretty late.

446
00:21:36,680 --> 00:21:37,480
How about this:

447
00:21:37,559 --> 00:21:38,480
You all keep chatting.

448
00:21:38,480 --> 00:21:39,000
As for me,

449
00:21:39,000 --> 00:21:40,000
I'll be heading off first.

450
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:40,279
Ah.

451
00:21:41,119 --> 00:21:41,480
Farewell.

452
00:21:41,480 --> 00:21:41,680
Don't go!

453
00:21:44,880 --> 00:21:45,279
Come on!

454
00:21:46,359 --> 00:21:47,160
Hey!

455
00:21:47,440 --> 00:21:48,240
Come on!

456
00:21:52,039 --> 00:21:54,160
I told you, you can't out-drink me.

457
00:21:54,480 --> 00:21:54,880
Hmm.

458
00:21:56,440 --> 00:21:57,039
Hey, Prince Liu Lie,

459
00:21:59,000 --> 00:21:59,279
Uh,

460
00:21:59,319 --> 00:22:01,279
about returning to the palace as emperor,

461
00:22:01,279 --> 00:22:02,799
could you reconsider it, please?

462
00:22:02,799 --> 00:22:03,680
No more reconsidering.

463
00:22:04,279 --> 00:22:05,640
Unless I win the tournament,

464
00:22:06,039 --> 00:22:07,640
I'm not going anywhere.

465
00:22:08,039 --> 00:22:09,200
Then we'll help you out.

466
00:22:09,599 --> 00:22:11,400
I appreciate your kind offer,

467
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:13,720
but I must rely on my own strength

468
00:22:13,720 --> 00:22:14,400
to win the tournament.

469
00:22:15,599 --> 00:22:17,200
Is winning or losing really that important?

470
00:22:29,039 --> 00:22:30,880
Even though the old emperor is dead,

471
00:22:32,279 --> 00:22:34,240
I still need to prove to him

472
00:22:34,640 --> 00:22:36,160
that when it comes to drinking,

473
00:22:36,480 --> 00:22:37,640
I'm better than him.

474
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:41,279
If I can beat that Masked God of Wine,

475
00:22:43,440 --> 00:22:44,279
then I've won.

476
00:22:44,599 --> 00:22:45,400
Brothers,

477
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:48,640
once we beat Liu Lie and the Masked God of Wine,

478
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:52,440
Duzun City will be ours!

479
00:22:52,440 --> 00:22:53,039
Hahahaha!

480
00:22:53,039 --> 00:22:53,839
Yes!

481
00:22:54,880 --> 00:23:01,160
The Ten!

482
00:23:01,160 --> 00:23:02,000
Uh, no, no, no.

483
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:02,480
Good sir,

484
00:23:02,480 --> 00:23:03,960
I'm not here to challenge you.

485
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:04,599
Then what

486
00:23:04,599 --> 00:23:05,680
are you here for?

487
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:11,279
I'm here to tell you

488
00:23:11,359 --> 00:23:12,440
where Liu Lie is.

489
00:23:12,680 --> 00:23:14,079
Hahahaha!

490
00:23:14,720 --> 00:23:14,880
Great!

491
00:23:36,079 --> 00:23:36,880
Halt!

492
00:23:37,640 --> 00:23:38,759
You step into the Wine Duel Arena,

493
00:23:38,759 --> 00:23:39,880
you have to drink.

494
00:23:40,160 --> 00:23:41,079
Hey, big bro, big bro.

495
00:23:41,079 --> 00:23:42,680
We're not here for a wine duel.

496
00:23:42,680 --> 00:23:44,079
I don't care what you're here for.

497
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:45,519
If you come and don't drink,

498
00:23:45,519 --> 00:23:46,480
leave your token behind.

499
00:23:46,880 --> 00:23:47,920
Move aside!

500
00:23:47,920 --> 00:23:48,640
We really have urgent business.

501
00:23:49,240 --> 00:23:50,279
Hey, big bro,

502
00:23:51,079 --> 00:23:52,759
cut us some slack here.

503
00:23:52,880 --> 00:23:54,119
Please, cut us some slack.

504
00:23:54,119 --> 00:23:55,000
No way.

505
00:23:55,000 --> 00:23:55,880
Hey!

506
00:23:56,759 --> 00:23:57,559
Hey, let him go!

507
00:23:58,680 --> 00:23:59,480
Let him go!

508
00:24:00,039 --> 00:24:00,880
Useless!

509
00:24:01,640 --> 00:24:02,480
Are you okay?

510
00:24:05,440 --> 00:24:06,039
Hahaha!

511
00:24:06,039 --> 00:24:06,880
Stop it!

512
00:24:08,960 --> 00:24:10,880
A bunch of kids who don't know their place.

513
00:24:11,079 --> 00:24:13,400
If you've got the guts, come at me together!

514
00:24:26,359 --> 00:24:27,319
Zhenzhen!

515
00:24:31,000 --> 00:24:31,920
Don't push yourself!

516
00:24:40,240 --> 00:24:41,160
You okay?

517
00:25:03,759 --> 00:25:04,559
Wow!

518
00:25:08,240 --> 00:25:09,039
Consort Zhen,

519
00:25:09,720 --> 00:25:13,039
I had no idea you could hold your liquor so well.

520
00:25:14,279 --> 00:25:15,240
Just goes to show our Zhenzhen

521
00:25:15,240 --> 00:25:16,200
hides her true talents.

522
00:25:16,359 --> 00:25:17,240
Right, Zhenzhen?

523
00:25:17,559 --> 00:25:18,599
This is nothing.

524
00:25:18,599 --> 00:25:20,240
This is nothing compared to my last visit here.

525
00:25:20,359 --> 00:25:22,480
You've been here before?

526
00:25:22,920 --> 00:25:23,440
Oh.

527
00:25:23,440 --> 00:25:24,720
Half the wine in Duzun City

528
00:25:24,720 --> 00:25:26,359
belongs to us, the Zhen family.

529
00:25:37,799 --> 00:25:39,480
The fight here is fierce.

530
00:25:43,880 --> 00:25:44,960
After searching so long,

531
00:25:45,559 --> 00:25:46,599
where on earth is he?

532
00:25:46,640 --> 00:25:48,319
Run, run!

533
00:25:50,920 --> 00:25:52,000
By the looks of it,

534
00:25:52,759 --> 00:25:54,559
that's gotta be the Masked God of Wine.

535
00:25:55,279 --> 00:25:56,119
I really want to know

536
00:25:56,119 --> 00:25:57,960
just how much this guy can drink.

537
00:25:58,519 --> 00:25:59,319
Huh?

538
00:26:03,559 --> 00:26:05,279
Hey, why isn't anyone here?

539
00:26:07,039 --> 00:26:09,039
Could he have already left?

540
00:26:09,319 --> 00:26:10,480
He's still here.

541
00:26:12,039 --> 00:26:13,200
How do you know?

542
00:26:15,440 --> 00:26:19,279
Because I can smell the wine getting stronger.

543
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:20,279
Smell of wine?

544
00:26:25,640 --> 00:26:26,640
I don't smell any wine.

545
00:26:33,279 --> 00:26:34,039
Hey!

546
00:26:34,920 --> 00:26:35,920
Masked God of Wine!

547
00:26:36,359 --> 00:26:39,240
Here are a few more little fools who don't know their place.

548
00:26:39,880 --> 00:26:41,200
Elder,

549
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:42,839
we're not here to drink with you.

550
00:26:43,039 --> 00:26:44,640
We want to take you somewhere.

551
00:26:44,759 --> 00:26:45,880
That won't do.

552
00:26:46,880 --> 00:26:48,200
I'm busy looking for someone.

553
00:26:48,359 --> 00:26:49,720
Are you looking for Liu Lie?

554
00:26:52,079 --> 00:26:53,400
You know where Liu Lie is?
